        " a",
        " previously",
        " unknown",
        " strain",
        " of",
        " coronavirus",
        ",",
        " that",
        " has",
        " spread",
        " quickly",
        " and",
        " still",
        " continues",
        " to",
        " fright",
        "en",
        " the",
        " world",
        ".\n",
